
-------------------------------------
|||| Jenkins PLugin Installation ||||
-------------------------------------


Default:
 - twister server side path: /opt/twister
 - twister client side path: /home/user/twister


	---- SERVER side ----

1. sudo cp /path/to/JenkinsPlugin/Jenkins/* /opt/twister/plugins

2. vim /path/to/twister/config/plugins.xml

append config:

<Plugin>
	<name>JENKINS</name>
	<jarfile>JenkinsPlugin.jar</jarfile>
	<pyfile>JenkinsPlugin.py</pyfile>
	<status>enabled</status>
</Plugin>

